svg.title: Seal of the County of Santa Clara, California

cc:Work.dc:title: Seal of the County of Santa Clara, California
cc:Work.dc:description: Seal of the County of Santa Clara, California, traced from a small GIF sample image. Color added, but not necessarily the "official" colors, if any were ever specified by the Santa Clara County Board of Supervisors. Manual tracing performed with Autocad R14; fills, color and line widths adjusted with Adobe Illustrator 9.0; final version created with Inkscape 0.47. Layer2 (locked) contains a monochrome version of the graphic. To access it, move the colorized seal aside or delete it.
